ZH: 这部法律适用于所有国民。
EN: This law applies to all citizens.

ZH: 国民的健康是国家的财富。
EN: The health of the citizens is the wealth of the nation.

ZH: 他是一个出色的国民。
EN: He is an outstanding citizen.

ZH: 我们应该关心国民的生活水平。
EN: We should care about the standard of living of the citizens.

ZH: 全国国民都在为国家的繁荣做出贡献。
EN: Citizens nationwide are contributing to the prosperity of the country.

ZH: 他是一位忠诚的国民。
EN: He is a loyal citizen.

ZH: 国民教育是每个国家的基石。
EN: National education is the cornerstone of every country.

ZH: 作为国民，我们需要爱护环境。
EN: As citizens, we need to cherish the environment.

ZH: 国民安全是政府的首要任务之一。
EN: National security is one of the government's top priorities.

ZH: 国民素质的提高是国家发展的必然要求。
EN: The improvement of the citizens' quality is an inevitable requirement for national development.

ZH: 每位国民都应该为社会做出贡献。
EN: Every citizen should contribute to society.

ZH: 他是这个国家的典范国民。
EN: He is an exemplary citizen of this country.

ZH: 国民的权利应该得到保障。
EN: The rights of the citizens should be protected.

ZH: 忠诚是每个国民应有的品质。
EN: Loyalty is a quality that every citizen should possess.

ZH: 国民经济的发展是国家的基础。
EN: The development of the national economy is the foundation of the country.

ZH: 我们应该为下一代国民留下一个更好的世界。
EN: We should leave a better world for the next generation of citizens.

ZH: 每位国民都应该尊重法律。
EN: Every citizen should respect the law.

ZH: 国民团结是国家繁荣的基础。
EN: National unity is the foundation of national prosperity.

ZH: 我们要团结一心，为国民利益而奋斗。
EN: We should unite and work for the interests of the citizens.

ZH: 我们应该教育国民尊重生命。
EN: We should educate the citizens to respect life.
